## App Router Dosya Konvansiyonlari
```
app/
├── layout.tsx              -> Root layout (html, body, providers)
├── page.tsx                -> Ana sayfa (/)
├── loading.tsx             -> Root Suspense boundary
├── error.tsx               -> Root error boundary ('use client')
├── not-found.tsx           -> 404 sayfasi
├── (auth)/                 -> Route group (URL'ye yansimaz)
│   ├── login/page.tsx
│   └── register/page.tsx
├── (dashboard)/
│   ├── layout.tsx          -> Dashboard layout (sidebar, nav)
│   └── inventory/
│       ├── page.tsx        -> Server Component (liste)
│       ├── loading.tsx     -> Skeleton
│       ├── [id]/page.tsx   -> Detay
│       └── new/page.tsx    -> Olusturma
├── api/webhooks/route.ts   -> Route Handler (sadece dis entegrasyon)
└── middleware.ts            -> Auth + i18n redirect
```

## Server Components vs Client Components
```
Karar Agaci:
├── Veri cekme (DB/API)?           -> Server Component (varsayilan)
├── Kullanici etkilesimi (onClick)? -> 'use client'
├── Browser API (localStorage)?     -> 'use client'
├── State / hooks (useState)?       -> 'use client'
├── Statik icerik / layout?         -> Server Component
├── Form submission?                -> Server Action
```
```tsx
async function InventoryPage({ searchParams }: { searchParams: Promise<{ q?: string }> }) {
  const { q } = await searchParams
  const items = await prisma.item.findMany({
    where: q ? { name: { contains: q, mode: 'insensitive' } } : undefined,
    orderBy: { createdAt: 'desc' },
    take: 50,
  })
  return (
    <PageContainer title="Envanter">
      <SearchBar defaultValue={q} />
      <Suspense fallback={<TableSkeleton rows={10} />}>
        <InventoryTable items={items} />
      </Suspense>
    </PageContainer>
  )
}
```

## Server Actions (Mutations)
```tsx
'use server'
import { revalidatePath } from 'next/cache'
import { redirect } from 'next/navigation'
import { z } from 'zod'

const createSchema = z.object({
  name: z.string().min(1).max(200),
  sku: z.string().regex(/^[A-Z]{2,4}-\d{3,6}$/),
  quantity: z.number().int().nonnegative(),
  warehouseId: z.string().uuid(),
})

export async function createItem(formData: FormData) {
  const session = await auth()
  if (!session?.user) throw new Error('Unauthorized')

  const parsed = createSchema.safeParse({
    name: formData.get('name'),
    sku: formData.get('sku'),
    quantity: Number(formData.get('quantity')),
    warehouseId: formData.get('warehouseId'),
  })
  if (!parsed.success) return { error: parsed.error.flatten().fieldErrors }

  await prisma.item.create({ data: { ...parsed.data, tenantId: session.user.tenantId } })
  revalidatePath('/inventory')
  redirect('/inventory')
}
```

## Data Fetching Stratejileri
```
├── Liste/detay?           -> Server Component + Prisma/fetch
├── Statik icerik?         -> generateStaticParams + ISR (revalidate: 60)
├── Dis API?               -> Route Handler (app/api/*)
├── Client-side realtime?  -> TanStack Query / SWR ('use client')
├── Form mutation?         -> Server Action + revalidatePath/revalidateTag
```

## State Yonetimi
```
Server state    -> React Server Components (DB'den dogrudan)
URL state       -> searchParams, useSearchParams (filtre, sayfa, siralama)
Form state      -> useActionState + Server Actions
Client UI state -> Zustand veya Jotai (minimal — sidebar, theme, modal)
Realtime state  -> TanStack Query ile polling veya WebSocket
```

## Database: Prisma ORM
```prisma
model Item {
  id          String   @id @default(cuid())
  tenantId    String   @map("tenant_id")
  name        String   @db.VarChar(200)
  sku         String   @unique
  quantity    Int      @default(0)
  isActive    Boolean  @default(true) @map("is_active")
  warehouseId String   @map("warehouse_id")
  warehouse   Warehouse @relation(fields: [warehouseId], references: [id])
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now()) @map("created_at")
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt @map("updated_at")
  @@index([tenantId])
  @@map("items")
}
```
- **Connection pooling:** Serverless → Prisma Accelerate veya PgBouncer; edge → `@prisma/adapter-neon`
- **Migration:** `npx prisma migrate dev --name add_items` — elle SQL YAZMA
- **Select:** `select: { id: true, name: true }` — tum tabloyu cekme; N+1 icin `include` kullan

## Auth: NextAuth.js v5
- `PrismaAdapter` ile DB-backed session/user
- `Credentials` provider: email/password; JWT callback ile `tenantId`, `role` token'a ekle
- `middleware.ts`: `export { auth as middleware } from '@/auth'` — tum route'lari koruma
- Session callback: `token.sub` → `session.user.id`; custom claim'ler (tenantId, role) session'a tasi
- ASLA secret'i client'a gonderme; `NEXTAUTH_SECRET` sadece server-side

## Test Stratejisi
```
├── Server Action / util?       -> Vitest (unit)
├── Client component?           -> Vitest + React Testing Library
├── API Route Handler?          -> Vitest + MSW
├── Full user flow?             -> Playwright (E2E)
```
```typescript
describe('createItem', () => {
  it('should reject invalid SKU', async () => {
    const formData = new FormData()
    formData.set('name', 'Test Item')
    formData.set('sku', 'invalid')
    formData.set('quantity', '10')
    formData.set('warehouseId', crypto.randomUUID())
    const result = await createItem(formData)
    expect(result?.error?.sku).toBeDefined()
  })
})
```

## Naming Conventions
| Oge | Format | Ornek |
|-----|--------|-------|
| Route klasoru | kebab-case | `inventory-items/` |
| Page / Layout | lowercase | `page.tsx`, `layout.tsx` |
| Component dosya | PascalCase | `InventoryTable.tsx` |
| Server Action | camelCase | `inventoryActions.ts` |
| Prisma model | PascalCase singular | `Item`, `Warehouse` |
| DB table (`@@map`) | snake_case plural | `items`, `warehouses` |
| DB column (`@map`) | snake_case | `tenant_id`, `created_at` |
| Env variable | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE | `DATABASE_URL`, `NEXTAUTH_SECRET` |

## Anti-Pattern'ler
| Anti-Pattern | Dogru Yaklasim |
|---|---|
| Her component'e `'use client'` | Varsayilan Server Component; sadece interaksiyon gerekiyorsa client |
| Client Component'te DB cagrisi | Server Component veya Server Action kullan |
| `fetch` + `useEffect` (client) | Server Component fetch veya TanStack Query |
| Route Handler her CRUD icin | Server Actions; Route Handler sadece webhook/dis API |
| `getServerSideProps` (Pages Router) | App Router + async Server Component |
| `router.push` sonrasi cache stale | `revalidatePath()` / `revalidateTag()` Server Action icinde |
| Prisma client global'de birden fazla | Singleton: `globalThis.prisma ??= new PrismaClient()` |
| Middleware'de agir islem (DB call) | Middleware hafif: JWT decode + redirect; DB → route/action |
| `any` type Server Action return | Zod schema + typed return `{ error: FieldErrors }` |
| Secret'lari client bundle'a koyma | `NEXT_PUBLIC_` SADECE public degerler; secret `.env.local` + server-only |
| Layout icinde searchParams kullanma | `searchParams` sadece `page.tsx`; layout'a prop veya client hook |

